<text xml:lang="ta" type="edition">
  <body>
    <div rend="parallel">
      <lg xml:id="Aink380">
<l>atta nīḷiṭai yavaṉoṭu pōkiya</l>
<l>muttēr veṇpaṉ mukiḻnakai maṭavara</l>
<l>ṟāya reṉṉum peyarē vallā</l>
<l>ṟeṭuttēṉ maṉṟa yāṉē</l>
<l>koṭuttōr maṉṟavava ḷāyat tōrē</l>
      </lg>
     <lg type="translation" xml:lang="en">
<l>[My] name is mother of the naïve girl  </l>
<l>with a smile of many white jasmine buds resembling pearls, </l>
<l>who went with him through the long paths. </l>
<l>I accepted [this] strong path. </l>
<l>Those who gave are her friends. </l>
      </lg>
    </div>
